<p>The Vertical Hour</h1></p>

<p>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</p>


<ref class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</ref>
<ref class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</ref>
<p>The Vertical Hour is a play by <ref class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/David_Hare_(dramatist)" title="David Hare (dramatist)">David Hare</ref>. The play addresses the relationship of characters with opposing views on the <ref target="/wiki/2003_invasion_of_Iraq" title="2003 invasion of Iraq">2003 invasion of Iraq</ref>, and also explores psychological tension between public lives and private lives.<ref target="#cite_note-1">[1]</ref></p>

